# 📊 Online Sales Data Analysis (SQL Project)
## 📌 Project Overview
This SQL project focuses on analyzing an online sales dataset to perform data cleaning, detect anomalies, and extract meaningful business insights
## 🎯 Objectives
- Identify and handle missing (NULL) values  
- Detect duplicate transaction records  
- Analyze payment methods used by customers  
- Identify top-selling and second-highest selling products  

---

## 📂 Dataset Details
- Database Used: `sales`
- Tables:
  - `Online Sales Data`
  - `online_sales_data2`
📈 Key Insights
Missing values were found in the region column and handled
Duplicate transaction IDs were identified
Most frequently used payment methods were analyzed
Top-selling and second-highest selling products were identified
## 📊 Data Dictionary

### 📁 Table: Online Sales Data

| Column Name      | Data Type | Description |
|-----------------|----------|------------|
| Transaction_ID  | INT      | Unique ID for each transaction |
| Product_Name    | VARCHAR  | Name of the product sold |
| Product_Category| VARCHAR  | Category of the product |
| Units_Sold      | INT      | Number of units sold |
| Unit_Price      | DECIMAL  | Price per unit |
| Total_Revenue   | DECIMAL  | Total revenue generated |
| Region          | VARCHAR  | Sales region (can contain NULL values) |
| Payment_Method  | VARCHAR  | Payment method used (Cash, Card, UPI, etc.) |
| Order_Date      | DATE     | Date of transaction |

---

### 📁 Table: online_sales_data2

| Column Name     | Data Type | Description |
|----------------|----------|------------|
| Transaction_ID | INT      | Transaction ID (Foreign Key) |
| Customer_ID    | INT      | Unique customer identifier |
| Customer_Name  | VARCHAR  | Name of the customer |
| Payment_Method | VARCHAR  | Payment method used |
| Order_Status   | VARCHAR  | Status of order (Completed, Pending, Cancelled) |
