### Q1- --Q1-find null value ?
---sql
select * from [Online Sales Data] where region is null;
---no null values 
---

### Q2 replace null value with 1 if u have ?
--sql
update [Online Sales Data] set region =123 where region is null;
---update null value with 1 
---
### Q3 finding dublicate values ?
---sql
select Transaction_ID, COUNT(*) dublicate_id  FROM [Online Sales Data] group by Transaction_ID  having count(*)>1;
---No any duplicate values 
---

### Q4 how many types of payment-method used ?
---sql
select Payment_Method ,count(*)as total_payment_by from [Online Sales Data] group by Payment_Method;
---120	Credit Card
---40	Debit Card
---80	PayPal
