### Q6 2ND HIGHEST PRODUCT SOLD ?
---sql
SELECT Product_Name,Units_Sold FROM (SELECT Product_Name,Units_Sold, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY Units_Sold DESC) AS rnk from [Online Sales Data])T where rnk=2;
---Yeti Rambler Tumbler	6
Nike Air Force 1	6
Spalding NBA Street Basketball	6
Gap Essential Crewneck T-Shirt	6
---
### Q7 TOP 3 HIGHEST PRODUCT SOLD WITH REVENUE ?
----sql
SELECT TOP 3  Product_Category, Product_name, SUM(Total_Revenue) as totam_amount_revecived from [Online Sales Data] group by Product_Category, Product_Name ORDER BY totam_amount_revecived DESC;
